Package: XLConnectXTRA
Title: Extends XLConnect in an opinionated way for templated Excel reporting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brandon", "Farr", , "bcfcodes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convenience functions for working with Excel "reporting" templates.
    Assumes a workflow beginning with an Excel report template with named
    ranges. An R script will build up reportable items and then call these
    convenience functions to simply and consistently write reporting data
    to proper template locations.
